'''睡眠盒子'''（{{lang-en|'''Sleep box'''}}）是一種極小型的住宿設備，為旅客提供經濟實惠的空間來[[睡眠|睡眠]]。<ref name="新華">{{cite web|url=http://ccnews.people.com.cn/n/2012/0716/c141677-18525479.html|title=舒服!"睡眠盒子"亮相内地机场|author=[[新華網|新華網]]|date=2012-07-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130406221649/http://ccnews.people.com.cn/n/2012/0716/c141677-18525479.html|archivedate=2013-04-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com.cn/24hour/n/2013/0206/c25408-20443471.html |title=“睡眠盒子”让出行更经济 |author=[[人民網|人民網]] |date=2013-02-06 |access-date=2013-06-24 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055632/http://www.people.com.cn/24hour/n/2013/0206/c25408-20443471.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=TL /> 睡眠盒子不同於膠囊旅館，後者空間更小且大多分佈於日本。<ref name=FOD>[http://www.fodors.com/news/story_2357.html "Pod Hotels: Small, Stylish, and Cheap"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fodors.com/news/story_2357.html |date=20150714162650 }} Fodor's, December 31, 2007</ref>

==商標==
“Sleepbox”是Arch Group的商標名，其他類似商標還有[[YOtel|YOtel]]、[[easyHotel|easyHotel]]、[[Qbic_Hotels|Qbic Hotels]]、Napcabs、Minutes Suites和SnoozeCub等。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mediaindonesia.com/mediatravelista/index.php/read/2012/07/28/4120/5/5-Hotel-Mikro-yang-Populer-di-Dunia |title=5 Hotel Mikro yang Populer di Dunia |date=July 28, 2012 |access-date=2013-06-24 |archive-date=2013-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130426051435/http://www.mediaindonesia.com/mediatravelista/index.php/read/2012/07/28/4120/5/5-Hotel-Mikro-yang-Populer-di-Dunia |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==設備==
睡眠盒子里的設備可能包括一張小床、[[通風設備|通風設備]]、[[鬧鐘|鬧鐘]]、網絡電視、電腦桌、[[LED燈|LED燈]]和梳粧檯等等。<ref name="新華"/><ref name=TL>Shields, Ann: [http://www.travelandleisure.com/travel-blog/carry-on/2011/9/16/how-to-sleep-comfortably-in-an-airport-terminal "How to Sleep Comfortably in an Airport Terminal"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.travelandleisure.com/travel-blog/carry-on/2011/9/16/how-to-sleep-comfortably-in-an-airport-terminal |date=20130127111129 }} Travel + Leisure, September 16, 2011</ref>

2011年，[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]的一家機場開設了睡眠盒子以提供旅客以休憩服務，<ref name=BBC>Trott, Russell: [http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14514816 "Sweet dreams? 'Sleep Box' opens at Moscow airport"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14514816 |date=20170308013642 }} BBC, August 13, 2011</ref> 每小時收費15美元。<ref name=TL />

2012年7月10日，[[西安|西安]][[咸陽國際機場|咸陽國際機場]]成為中國第一家開設睡眠盒子的機場，每個睡眠盒子大小為3平方米。<ref name="新華"/>

